Well thank you for advising me on a post where I did state,”I need help”

I didn’t ask where to find weed 🤔are you a cop bud? I asked to speak with individuals who partake in the cultivation and transportation of cannabis. Said individuals may read this and What happens there after is in my dms 😉

A friend of a friend committed suicide a year ago and everyone was wondering why nobody was close to him. He had friends, a gf and nice things.....they meant nothing to him. No to say I understand suicidal but death is inevitable and if you truly hate yours , who am I to say you are wrong for ending it? Be happy if you can but don’t put yourself through more and more pain just to say “I lived with it”
I appreciate all of you so much
